org.cloudgraph.hbase.filter

Class InitialFetchColumnFilterAssembler

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cloudgraph.hbase.filter.FilterListAssembler
      • org.cloudgraph.hbase.filter.InitialFetchColumnFilterAssembler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Assembler, HBaseFilterAssembler

    public class InitialFetchColumnFilterAssembler
extends FilterListAssembler
    Creates an HBase column filter set based on the given criteria which leverages the HBase MultipleColumnPrefixFilter to return only columns for the graph root as well as any columns associated with type nodes linked through one of more singular relations.
    Since:
    0.5
    Author:
    Scott Cinnamond
    See Also:
